Package name.pehl.piriti.rebind.propertyhandler

Interface Summary
PropertyHandler Interface for generating code for one property.
PropertyHandlerRegistry Registry to find PropertyHandlers based on a PropertyContext.
 

Class Summary
AbstractArrayPropertyHandler Abstract PropertyHandler for arrays.
AbstractCollectionPropertyHandler Abstract PropertyHandler for collections.
AbstractConverterPropertyHandler PropertyHandler implementation which uses a Converter from the ConverterRegistry.
AbstractEnumPropertyHandler Abstract PropertyHandler for enum types.
AbstractPropertyHandler Abstract base class for PropertyHandlers which contains common code.
AbstractRegistryPropertyHandler Abstract PropertyHandler implementation for types with an own reader.
PropertyAnnotation<T extends Annotation> Helper class for one annotated property.
PropertyContext Class which contains information needed to generate code for the evaluation, conversion and assignment of a property.
VariableNames  
 

Enum Summary
ReferenceType Describes the type of reference type of one property mapped by @Json or @Xml.
